nodes.text: A non-sentient space-borne creature that existed in the galaxy. At least one was present in the Typhonic Nebula during 35 ABY. It ate First Order TIE fighters as the Millennium Falcon narrowly escaped it. Its characteristics seem to be a long, snakelike body and a large mouth, formed by flaps of rough skin stretched over three large tusks. At least one resides in Megafauna Chasm.
